# POS backend API

This workspace (`posfont`) is the **Angular frontend only**.

The **backend API** is a separate Spring Boot / Kotlin project:

**`f:/src/pos/api/pos`**

- Package root: `me.pixka.pos`
- Default URL: `http://localhost:8080` (see `src/app/app.config.ts` → `POS_API_BASE_URL`)
- Run: `cd f:/src/pos/api/pos && mvn spring-boot:run`
- Tests: `cd f:/src/pos/api/pos && mvn test`

When changing API behaviour, entities, or DTOs, edit the **backend** at `f:/src/pos/api/pos`, then mirror types and HTTP calls in this frontend.

**Read first:** `f:/src/pos/api/pos/NOTIFY-FRONTEND.md` (checklist + Angular file mapping).

| Backend | Frontend (this repo) |
|---------|----------------------|
| `f:/src/pos/api/pos` | `f:/src/pos/posfont` |
| `*/model/*.kt`, `*/api/*Request.kt` | `src/app/*/*.model.ts` |
| `*/api/*Controller.kt` | `src/app/*/*.service.ts` |
